  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I just did a test installing the latest React InstantSearch and I get preact 10.28.2, so this is an issue with your own lockfile you can solve by updating (`yarn upgrade preact` for example)\n\n```\ninstantsearch.js@4.86.1:\n  version \"4.86.1\"\n  resolved \"https://registry.yarnpkg.com/instantsearch.js/-/instantsearch.js-4.86.1.tgz#eb6a608e84324f96a2e9a2cf6830023416a20675\"\n  integrity sha512-ETazkxnWj3aOsHgQem1JQ4roqhfpkA32CZEW+ccP+rQqSbO4sCEEMJTy1A1BMiTD1iCoBFWD+x+8Bx73DOm/Gg==\n  dependencies:\n    \"@algolia/events\" \"^4.0.1\"\n    \"@types/dom-speech-recognition\" \"^0.0.1\"\n    \"@types/google.maps\" \"^3.55.12\"\n    \"@types/hogan.js\" \"^3.0.0\"\n    \"@types/qs\" \"^6.5.3\"\n    ai \"^5.0.18\"\n    algoliasearch-helper \"3.27.0\"\n    hogan.js \"^3.0.2\"\n    htm \"^3.0.0\"\n    instantsearch-ui-components \"0.16.0\"\n    preact \"^10.10.0\"\n    qs \"^6.5.1\"\n    react \">= 0.14.0\"\n    search-insights \"^2.17.2\"\n    zod \"^3.25.76 || ^4\"\n    zod-to-json-schema \"3.24.6\"\n\n...\n\nreact-instantsearch-core@7.22.1:\n  version \"7.22.1\"\n  resolved \"https://registry.yarnpkg.com/react-instantsearch-core/-/react-instantsearch-core-7.22.1.tgz#92cffbfa5c661b55d546ffc2284416bca364671b\"\n  integrity sha512-fumuQbLKzEnZ3pX9LHXCbxfol8OiStWa63ujDin9SMb2k6cCMXbkuRC/eRe1EDLYPSfkVAKV+r6elOwT6fTVYQ==\n  dependencies:\n    \"@babel/runtime\" \"^7.27.6\"\n    ai \"^5.0.18\"\n    algoliasearch-helper \"3.27.0\"\n    instantsearch.js \"4.86.1\"\n    use-sync-external-store \"^1.0.0\"\n    zod \"^3.25.76 || ^4\"\n    zod-to-json-schema \"3.24.6\"\n\nreact-instantsearch@^7.22.1:\n  version \"7.22.1\"\n  resolved \"https://registry.yarnpkg.com/react-instantsearch/-/react-instantsearch-7.22.1.tgz#7ce1b09d0765db291d480851eee24a0d3a705647\"\n  integrity sha512-sTZ8z2JcSyveP0RmClmP9KFkJMQ9ZZmZKI05uSmfx7fP21N8Ry9CCyn2EvalGFm2gTPaB7VMFZrC9q7HXvG9wA==\n  dependencies:\n    \"@babel/runtime\" \"^7.27.6\"\n    instantsearch-ui-components \"0.16.0\"\n    instantsearch.js \"4.86.1\"\n    react-instantsearch-core \"7.22.1\"\n\n...\n\npreact@^10.10.0:\n  version \"10.28.2\"\n  resolved \"https://registry.yarnpkg.com/preact/-/preact-10.28.2.tgz#4b668383afa4b4a2546bbe4bd1747e02e2360138\"\n  integrity sha512-lbteaWGzGHdlIuiJ0l2Jq454m6kcpI1zNje6d8MlGAFlYvP2GO4ibnat7P74Esfz4sPTdM6UxtTwh/d3pwM9JA==\n```\n\n\nreminder: if you're using React InstantSearch, this dependency is nowhere in your actual code, so the warning is a false positive one.",
